data.description: This beautiful home features one of our most popular floor plans. You'll find 9-ft. ceilings and a generous open great room with surround sound pre-wiring. The gourmet kitchen offers 42-in. upper cabinets in Linen color, a gas cooktop and double ovens. The master bath boasts a large marble shower in lieu of a tub, and executive-height cabinets. Additional features include tile flooring throughout with lush carpeting in the bedrooms, and a whole-home water softener. This ENERGY STAR® certified home is move-in ready. MLS#21825989
